g.aria-label: Initialize counter to two. Flag counter and return to number. Check if the input is one (edge case). Check if the number is empty. Decrement number and return to counter. Decrement counter and return to number. Go to first black number cell. Erase flag and fill counter. Fill number and return to counter. Check if counter is empty. Counter is full (edge case). Fill and increment counter. Decide primality based on counter flag.
This machine determines if the number N of black cells is prime by trial division.
